<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idb7d465f8-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1981-01-01">Jan. 1, 1981</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/96/354/s4">section 4 of Pub. L. 96–354</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t5/s601">section 601 of this title</ref>.</p>
